      <title>美国称英国亿万富翁刘易斯因内幕消息应得到宽大处理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/uk-billionaire-lewis-deserves-leniency-for-insider-tips-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官在本周晚些时候对 87 岁的英国亿万富翁乔·刘易斯 (Joe Lewis) 宣判前告诉一名联邦法官，他将因向私人飞行员和女友传递公司秘密信息而受到不到一年半的监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/uk-billionaire-lewis-deserves-leniency-for-insider-tips-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
